    `,keyTakeaways:["SOC careers progress from L1 through specializations and leadership","Certifications validate skills - start with Security+ or BTL1","Free platforms like TryHackMe and LetsDefend provide hands-on practice","Daily learning habits compound into significant growth over time","Community involvement accelerates learning and opens opportunities"],additionalResources:[{title:"TryHackMe",type:"tool",url:"https://tryhackme.com"},{title:"LetsDefend",type:"tool",url:"https://letsdefend.io"},{title:"CyberDefenders",type:"tool",url:"https://cyberdefenders.org"}]},{id:"10.4",courseId:"soc-fundamentals",title:"Course Summary & Next Steps",content:`
